{"tid":1012017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新年要嘗試寵物美容新趨勢嗎? 蛋蛋塗亮粉","createTime":"2019-02-07T08:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T09:38:06.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3271042a665a1375356bbc12b10d1d74b090bcea","tid":1012017,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:48:13.000Z","msg":"美國寵物社群媒體最近出現新話題：寵物狗蛋蛋抹上亮粉，這種裝飾引起熱烈討論，正反意見都有。<br />\n一名寵物美容業者在臉書表示，做這一行，自以為看過很多怪事，早已見怪不怪，但現在卻看到亮粉蛋蛋。<br />\n北卡羅萊納州寵物美容院Royal Paws Pet Salon 也分享亮粉蛋蛋照片，不過，老闆澄清，純粹只是讓顧客知道這個新熱潮，他們的店並未提供這種服務。<br />\n有些人批評把狗蛋染色的飼主，甚至有人質疑，亮粉會影響公狗的健康。讓狗蛋蛋染色的飼主說明，這種亮粉以玉米澱粉製作，吃下去也不會造成傷害。<br />\n有網友開玩笑，公狗舔蛋蛋把亮粉吃下去之後，如果在屋內亂拉屎，就證據確鑿。另一女網友開玩笑說，反正公狗會舔亮粉，不如把亮粉弄得美味一點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/03/realtime/5884649.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F03%2Frealtime%2F5884649.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=17ee8b47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有隻公狗的蛋蛋塗上藍色亮粉。 取自groomeryfoolery臉書帳號<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3630213?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F3630213%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcrhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=bc5de692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3630213?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"ff4c6969ef7d4b1389508468ae54efbd286b546f","tid":1012017,"uid":173239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:50:57.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"4c42ee6a15b650761ba2a39e04182a3f12add749","tid":1012017,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"幾時染鳩毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977b561c99b2d1eacb7dfa8d5229d0